### Local Storage Strategy
The context uses localStorage for persistence with smart data management:

```typescript
// Strip large data (base64 images) before storing
function stripLargeData(assignment: Assignment): Assignment {
  return {
    ...assignment,
    questions: assignment.questions.map(q => ({
      ...q,
      scenarioImage: q.scenarioImage?.startsWith('data:image') ? null : q.scenarioImage
    }))
  }
}

