## Storage & Performance

### LocalStorage Management
The system implements sophisticated localStorage management:
- **Quota monitoring**: Tracks storage usage
- **Automatic cleanup**: Removes large data when needed
- **Graceful degradation**: Falls back to minimal data storage
- **Error recovery**: Handles quota exceeded scenarios

### Data Optimization
- **Lazy loading**: Only load assignments when needed
- **Image optimization**: Strip base64 images from stored data
- **Selective persistence**: Store only essential data long-term

